      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92), a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the high-revving S65 V8 engine, utilizing eight individual throttle bodies to achieve its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal longitudinal traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a flat cornering attitude without compromising compliance. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory finish remains original and unblemished, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous care.",
